MENU FILE HEADER (Don't delete)
MENU FILE NAME: $popcontrib/x/xved/doit_menus/menus/dired_menu
FACILITIES FOR GETING A LIST OF FILES
POINTING AT THEM AND DOING THINGS
Start a "dired" file. (Give pattern or *)   !!      ENTER 'dired '
Get file in "read only" mode (like pved)    !!      'dired -rv'

Get file or expand directory                !!      menu_dired_command(%"ved_dired"%)
Do so after quitting current file           !!      menu_dired_command(%"ved_qdired"%)

Compile the file                            !!      'dired -load'
Remove "expanded" directory                 !!      vedchardown <> veddo(%'dired -dcd'%)
Remove file named on current line           !!      ENTER 'dired -rm'
Recursive remove                            !!      ENTER 'dired -rm-r'
Remove directory                            !!      ENTER 'dired -rmdir'
Rename file (give new full name)            !!      ENTER 'dired -mv '
Copy file (give new full name)              !!      ENTER 'dired -cp '
Rename in same directory (give new name)    !!      ENTER 'dired -mvd '
Copy in same directory (give new name)      !!      ENTER 'dired -cpd '
Get long listing (ls -l) for files named    !!      'dired -l'
Get long chronological listing (-lt)        !!      'dired -lt'
Change mode of the file                     !!      ENTER 'dired -chmod '

INFORMATION on "dired"                      !!      'help ved_dired'
Menu menu           ---->                   !!      'menu menu_menu'
